        "description": {
            "name": "description",
            "type": "java.lang.String",
            "value": "Currency formatting isn't correct when using nl_BE as locale.\r\n\r\nZend_Registry::set('Zend_Currency', new Zend_Currency('nl_BE'));\r\n$this->currency(50);\r\nGives as result:\r\n50,00 \u20ac\r\n\r\nThis should be:\r\n\u20ac 50,00\r\n\r\nHowever when using nl_NL as locale the formatting is correct.\r\n\r\nFix:\r\n\/Locale\/Data\/nl_BE.xml\r\n\r\nChange currencyFormat > pattern to:\r\n<pattern>\u00a4#,##0.00<\/pattern>"
        },
