                    "body": "According to CLDR the format to use for currencies is >#,##0.00 \u00a4<\r\n\r\nThis means that ZF produces the correct output.\r\nWhen you wish to use another output simply give the wished format.\r\nWhen you feel that there is an error within CLDR please report an issue at http:\/\/cldr.unicode.org\r\n\r\nYou should note that even the actual release of CLDR which is 3 weeks old, provides the same format pattern.",
